commitResults.messageBody: Case insensitive keyword "list" is used to list out all the task

commitResults.messageTitle: feat: Create Task.java for task encapsulation
commitResults.messageBody: Task class is incomplete, but contains enough information for a task
FastScanner class is an abstraction on top of Java io standard library which provides useful methods for parsing user inputs in a fast, efficient and simplified way.
Additional methods are added to Task.java to manage the task completion
Deadline, Event and Todo classes  were added which are subclass of Task

commitResults.messageTitle: chore: Add spacing to Event toString
feat: Add additional useful functions to FastScanner
commitResults.messageBody:
nextUntil reads the user input till a specified delimiter. The delimiter is ignored, like String.split()

remainingLine reads the remaining string in a lline, useful to handle the cursor like functionalities of FastScanner functions
